---
title: Pricing
layout: layouts/base.njk
permalink: /pricing/
layout_script: assets/js/pricing.js
---

{% import "macros/blocks.njk" as blocks %}

<article class="container">
    <div class="hero">
        <h1>Kick the margin moochers to the curb</h1>
    </div>

    <section>
        <div class="block block--img-left">
            <div class="block__img">
                <p class="block__body">What’s your estimated monthly revenue from online sales?</p>

                <table class="pricing__comparison">
                    <tr>
                        <th colspan="2">
                            <div class="slider" min="1000" max="25000" step="500" value="10000"></div>
                        </th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th>{{ site.images.logo | svgContents("pricing__logo") | safe }}</th>
                        <th>
                            <p class="plan__price">
                                <strong id="kamfly-price">€ 300</strong>
                                <span>/ month</span>
                            </p>
                        </th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th>{{ "/assets/thuisbezorgd.svg" | svgContents("pricing__logo") | safe }}</th>
                        <th>
                            <p class="plan__price">
                                <strong id="thuisbezorgd-price">€ 1.300</strong>
                                <span>/ month</span>
                            </p>
                        </th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th>{{ "/assets/ubereats.svg" | svgContents("pricing__logo") | safe }}</th>
                        <th>
                            <p class="plan__price">
                                <strong id="ubereats-price">€ 1.500</strong>
                                <span>/ month</span>
                            </p>
                        </th>
                    </tr>
                </table>

                <button class="link block__link">How this is calculated</button>
            </div>

            <div class="block__content">
                <h2 class="block__title">Protect your profits.</h2>
                <p class="block__body">Every restaurant should be able to offer online ordering without giving up their profit margin. Some of our compeition charge as much as 15% of TOTAL sales, but it doesn’t have to be that expensive.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="alt">
        <div class="block">
            <div class="block__content">
                <h2 class="block__title">Kamfly Premium Plans.</h2>
                <p class="block__body">We offer fair, scalable pricing plans to fit your restaurant’s needs.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="pricing">
                <div class="pricing__plan">
                    <h3 class="plan__title">Standard</h3>
                    <p class="plan__price">
                        <strong>€ 25</strong>
                        <span>/ month</span>
                        <br>
                        <em>per location</em>
                    </p>

                    <hr>

                    <ul class="plan__features">
                        <li class="plan__feature">Custom online menus</li>
                        <li class="plan__feature">QR codes for contactless menus</li>
                        <li class="plan__feature">Use your logos and accent color</li>
                        <li class="plan__feature">Admin site for updating your menus</li>
                        <li class="plan__feature">Unlimited number of locations</li>
                    </ul>

                    <a class="btn btn--hollow" href="/get-started?plan=standard">get started</a>
                </div>
                <div class="pricing__plan pricing__plan--highlighted">
                    <h3 class="plan__title">Pro</h3>
                    <p class="plan__price">
                        <strong>€ 100</strong>
                        <span>/ month</span>
                        <br>
                        <em>per location</em>
                    </p>
                    <p>+</p>
                    <p class="plan__price">
                        <strong>2%</strong>
                        <span>/ transaction</span>
                        <br>
                        <em>+ Payment gateway fees</em>
                    </p>

                    <hr>

                    <ul class="plan__features">
                        <li class="plan__feature">
                            <strong>All Standard plan features</strong>
                        </li>
                        <li class="plan__feature">Online ordering via Snipcart</li>
                        <li class="plan__feature">Customer accounts</li>
                        <li class="plan__feature">Customer dashboard</li>
                        <li class="plan__feature">Online ordering analytics</li>
                    </ul>

                    <a class="btn btn--primary" href="/get-started?plan=pro">get started</a>
                </div>
                <div class="pricing__plan">
                    <h3 class="plan__title">Custom</h3>
                    <p class="plan__price">
                        <strong>ASK</strong>
                        <span>/ contact us</span>
                        <br>
                        <em>for details</em>
                    </p>

                    <hr>

                    <ul class="plan__features">
                        <li class="plan__feature">Integration with your point-of-sale system</li>
                        <li class="plan__feature">Build and design your custom site</li>
                        <li class="plan__feature">Online & social media marketing</li>
                        <li class="plan__feature">Search engine optimiation</li>
                    </ul>

                    <a class="btn btn--hollow" href="/get-started?plan=custom">get started</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <div class="block block--img-left">
            {{ blocks.blockImage("/images/blocks/food-delivery.jpg", "Delivery driver picking up an order") }}
            <div class="block__content">
                <h2 class="block__title">What about food delivery?</h2>
                <p class="block__body">Our mission is to provide the online experience that your customers want. You know your business, your team, and your brand and we want you to be empowered with the control of the full customer experience. Our goal is to provide a polished online ordering experience at a price that allows you to create jobs for delivery drivers that represent your business.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="alt">
        <div class="block block--img-right">
            {{ blocks.blockImage("/images/blocks/menus.png", "Kamfly menus showing the light and dark theme options") }}
            <div class="block__content">
                <h2 class="block__title">Kamfly grows with your business.</h2>
                <p class="block__body">Not ready to offer online ordering? No problem! With our Standard plan you will get an online menu that looks great on every device and can replace paper menus with QR codes. Update your menu without reprinting, and when you're ready it only takes a few steps to enable online ordering.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</article>